na caitac chakyam, tāvataś carmaṇo 'bhāvāt, bhāve 'pi chādanasyāśakyatvāt. upāyena punaḥ śakyam. upānahaś carmaṇā kevalena sarvā bhūmiś chāditā bhavati.

<commentary>dṛṣṭāntoktam arthaṃ prakṛte yojayan nāha.

śatruprabhṛtayo bhāvā mayā vārayitum aśakyāḥ. tadvat medinīcarmacchādanavad apakārakriyāyāḥ. ataḥ svacittam eva śakyaṃ vārayiṣyāmi. anyavāraṇasyāpārthakatvāt, svacittavāraṇād eva tatsiddheḥ. tasmāt sā cittam eva.</commentary>

vīryapāramitā tu kuśalotsāhasvabhāvātivispaṣṭaṃ cittam evety āha. vacanakāyasahitasyāpi cittasya kuśalapakṣe mandapracārasya na tādṛśaṃ phalamupajāyate, yādṛśaṃ dhyānādiviṣaye paṭupravṛtter ekākino 'pi cittasya phalaṃ brahmabhūyādikam. tasmāt sā cittam eva.